st|color={{fire color}}|area=Cave: [[Rugged Flats]]}}\n{{Availability/Entry1|1|v=PokéPark 2|link=PokéPark 2: Wonders Beyond|color={{grass color}}|area=[[Wish Park]]}}\n{{Availability/Entry1|1|v=MD GTI|link=Pokémon Mystery Dungeon: Gates to Infinity|color={{silver color}}|area=[[Great Glacier]] (1F-14F), [[Redland Reaches]] (1F-10F), [[Eastern Savanna]] (1F-14F)}}\n{{Availability/Entry1|1|v=Rumble U|color={{fire color}}|area=[[Vehicle Gallery#A Flowing Desert|Vehicle Gallery: A Flowing Desert]]}}\n|}\n|}\n{{Availability/Gen|gen=VI}}\n{{Availability/Entry1|1|v=Battle Trozei|color={{defense color}}|area=[[Dragon Hill#Stage 2|Dragon Hill: Stage 2]]}}\n{{Availability/Entry1|1|v=Shuffle|color={{beauty color}}|area=[[Wacky Workshop|Wacky Workshop: Stage 164]]}}\n{{Availability/Entry1|1|v=Rumble World|color={{fire color}}|area=[[Distortion Land#Withered Cemetery|Distortion Land: Withered Cemetery]] <small>(All Areas)</small>}}\n{{Availability/Entry1|1|v=Picross|color={{skill color light}}|area=[[Pokémon Picross Stages#Area 19|Area 19: Stage 05]]}}\n|}\n|}\n{{Availability/Footer}}\n\n===Held items===\n{{HeldItems\n|type=ghost\n|bw1=Spell Tag|bw1type=None|bw1rar=5\n|b2w21=Spell Tag|b2w21type=None|b2w21rar=5\n}}\n\n===Stats===\n====Base stats====\n{{BaseStats\n|type=Ghost\n|HP=38\n|Attack=30\n|Defense=85\n|SpAtk=55\n|SpDef=65\n|Speed=30}}\n\n===Type effectiveness===\n{{TypeEffectiveness\n|type1=Ghost\n|Normal=0\n|Fighting=0\n|Flying=100\n|Poison=50\n|Ground=100\n|Rock=100\n|Bug=50\n|Ghost=200\n|Steel=100\n|Fire=100\n|Water=100\n|Grass=100\n|Electric=100\n|Psychic=100\n|Ice=100\n|Dragon=100\n|Dark=200\n|Fairy=100\n|notes=yes\n|ghost=yes\n|newnormal=1\n|newfighting=1}}\n\n===Learnset===\n====By [[Level|leveling up]]====\n{{learnlist/levelh/7|Yamask|Ghost|Ghost|5}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Astonish|Ghost|Physical|30|100|15||\'\'\'}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Protect|Normal|Status|&mdash;|&mdash;|10}}\n{{learnlist/level7|5|Disable|Normal|Status|&mdash;|100|20}}\n{{learnlist/level7|9|Haze